Package org.pdxfinder.graph.dao

Class Sample

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pdxfinder.graph.dao.Sample
  • public class Sample
extends java.lang.Object
    Sample represents a piece of tissue taken from a specimen (human or mouse) A sample could be cancerous or not (tissue used to compare to cancer sampled from a health tissue)
